OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry at first with some bright
OL,6,Fspells. Turning increasingly cloudy
OL,7,Fand windy into the afternoon with the
OL,8,Fodd spot of rain. Mild in the brighter
OL,9,Fspells.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStorm Dave will bring gales
OL,12,Fthis evening with some heavy and
OL,13,Fblustery spells of rain. The storm
OL,14,Fwill clear in the early hours and
OL,15,Fwinds will ease.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FSunny spells and scattered
OL,18,Fshowers on Easter Day with lighter
OL,19,Fwinds. Feeling colder than previous
OL,20,Fdays with a fresh breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
